{{Infobox journal |title=Accountability in Research |impact=1.512 |impact-year=2016 |history=1989-present |frequency=bimonthly |language=English |abbreviation=Account. Res. |editor=Adil E. Shamoo |publisher=Taylor & Francis |website=http://www.tandfonline.com/loi/gacr20 |ISSN=0898-9621 |eISSN=1545-5815 |OCLC=17959730 |CODEN=ARQAEZ }}
'''''Accountability in Research''''' is a [[peer review|peer-reviewed]] [[academic journal]], published by [[Taylor & Francis]], examining systems for ensuring integrity in the conduct of biomedical research. The [[editor-in-chief]] is Adil E. Shamoo ([[University of Maryland School of Medicine]]).
